<plot>This short is one of the "Memories From Melody Lane" series that features the Music Makers. Four songs featuring the word "moon" in the title are presented. After each song is sung (the last using a clip from _Shine On Harvest Moon (1944)_ (qv) with 'Ann Sheridan' (qv)), the audience is invited to sing along. Lyrics are shown on title cards. For a complete list of songs, check the soundtrack listing.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?333598</url></doc>
